page_description: Learn how to use Azure OpenAI to control your deployments rate limits.
chunk_content: Migrating existing deploymentsAs part of the transition to the new quota system and TPM based allocation, all existing Azure OpenAI model deployments have been automatically migrated to use quota. In cases where the existing TPM/RPM allocation exceeds the default values due to previous custom rate-limit increases, equivalent TPM were assigned to the impacted deployments.
